@{
    ViewBag.Title = "About the Contest";
}
<style>
    p,li {
        font-size: 18px;
    }
</style>
<h2>@ViewBag.Title.</h2>
<h3 style="background-color: #6400a5; color: white;">@ViewBag.Message</h3>

<div class="text-center">
    <p>Talents Unleash is a talent show and skill exhibition aimed at discovering, showcasing and harnessing great talents and skills in across different fields of endeavors including entertainment, sports, science etc.</p>

    <p>
        The  focus is on  young people who may not have had any opportunity to bring their talent to the public domain and may not know how to apply their talents and skills to productive ventures.
    </p>

    <h3 style="background-color: #6400a5; color: white;">Mission</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>To discover and showcase great young talents in Nigerians.</li>
        <li>To inspire young Nigerians to unleash the greatness in them.</li>
        <li>To celebrate and promote Nigerian talents in various fields.</li>
        <li>To help budding entrepreneurs grow and provide jobs for the unemployed.</li>
        <li>To mentor and coach young talents to greatness.</li>
        <li>To guide young talents to productively engage their talents.</li>
    </ol>
</div>

